Package entity

Class AppointmentSlot

Object
AppointmentSlot
public class AppointmentSlot extends Object
Represents a time slot for an appointment with a doctor on a specific date. Each slot can either be available or booked, and contains the start time, end time, and the associated doctor.

  • Method Details

    • tryBook

      public boolean tryBook(Appointment appointment)
      Attempts to book this appointment slot for a given appointment. If the slot is already booked, the booking attempt will fail.
      Parameters:
      appointment - The appointment to book in the slot.
      Returns:
      true if the slot was successfully booked, false if it was already booked.
